# Logging Rules
- Always use `app/utils/log.js` wrapper - never console methods
- Import: `const { logError, logInfo, logWarn } = require('./utils/log')`
- Use appropriate levels: error, warn, info, debug
- Log files in `/logs` directory (excluded from git)
- If wrapper lacks a method, suggest adding it

```javascript
// Correct
logInfo('Processing image', imageId);
logError('API failed', error);

// Never
console.log('Processing');
```